{"tid":261854,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"各位.千奇唔好去爆x王","createTime":"2017-05-28T18:41:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T02:23:50.000Z","uid":119562,"like":43,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b1727791c2d7d5a1044c9620d65195e6c083225d","tid":261854,"uid":119562,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T18:41:50.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n千奇唔好去（爆x王）到整電話<br />\n佢話就話係原裝mon 係邊到廠拎返黎<br />\n其實就係你爆玻璃佢用機介左你塊液晶出黎<br />\n用加工整反落去塊新玻璃到<br />\n佢地買貨全部都係淘寶 同人講<span style=\"color: red;\">原廠訂</span><br />\n買返黎幾十蚊 幫你整一整就四百幾五百<br />\n<br />\n利申:做過幾日"},{"pid":"07eff2666aad9fc3274878409b69ec355c0bacb5","tid":261854,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T18:45:05.000Z","msg":"新之都？"},{"pid":"865278ba42c778f2d78fde322777a523a8f2f30f","tid":261854,"uid":119562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T18:47:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新之都？</blockquote><br />\n唔係 呢家有三間鋪 元朗 天水圍 屯門 觀塘開緊開埋就第四間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"042436fc9cad178ac960bdb0f23217f211d3b663","tid":261854,"uid":79023,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T18:49:31.000Z","msg":"其實間間都係咁做<br />\n無講出黎咁解姐"},{"pid":"c124d161a8e421bb5ebe4a0c374db135a5c57784","tid":261854,"uid":89712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T18:51:37.000Z","msg":"唯訊呢？"},{"pid":"c700316879046c2121db3279698265397fb91751","tid":261854,"uid":12510,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T18:52:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實間間都係咁做<br />\n無講出黎咁解姐</blockquote><br />\n遺反商品說明條例wo  ching"},{"pid":"b386ad9dbf92db965cafe932085ec88f64a6a70b","tid":261854,"uid":119562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-28T18:54:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實間間都係咁做<br />\n無講出黎咁解姐</blockquote