 />\n<br />\n但最多收你200-250  如果收超過400 一定係玻璃連液晶咁換 仲要係原裝液晶 400係個成本<br />\n<br />\n我真係好憎香港d手機維修店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"109c9e475452b593b66a0c0fe9e091804cf6fbd4","tid":261854,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T03:47:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唉 又一單黑店<br />\n我真係好想搞一間完全透明 既維修店   明碼實價 等大家唔洗比人昆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n爆玻璃係要用機整 但玻璃一定唔係原廠 因為原廠同唔係原廠都無乜分別<br />\n<br />\n但最多收你200-250  如果收超過400 一定係玻璃連液晶咁換 仲要係原裝液晶 400係個成本<br />\n<br />\n我真係好憎香港d手機維修店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 因為原廠同唔係原廠都無乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e0dea3276bba9953f51cfe89e8e48ba49a205cd","tid":261854,"uid":4241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T03:52:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>出面邊有全新原廠件<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪係 我諗唔會有人咁膠真係信掛<br />\n<br />\n就好似iphone電<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母間間都話原廠電 原你老母咩 <br />\n<br />\n買粒飛毛腿好過用假電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2f5c31941beef6a172d5ddcefb64ccad8daa326","tid":261854,"uid":60793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T03:53:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唉 又一單黑店<br />\n我真係好想搞一間完全透明 既維修店   明碼實價 等大家唔洗比人昆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n爆玻璃係要用機整 但玻璃一定唔係原廠 因為原廠同唔係原廠都無乜分別<br />\n<br />\n但最多收你200-250  如果收超過400 一定係玻璃連液晶咁換 仲要係原裝液晶 400係個成本<br />\n<br />\n我真係好憎香港d手機維修店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote