l/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n飛毛腿用左大半年都唔錯 , <br />\n<br />\n利申 自己換"},{"pid":"eac6fac6d33749a0fd5bd3d2c29c58186d236f4c","tid":261854,"uid":116704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T05:46:06.000Z","msg":"巴打，咁如果整mon/電去邊間整好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （唔識自己換）"},{"pid":"942a3bbabdcbf92e534073e5b2b14f5042ff8a36","tid":261854,"uid":12994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T05:49:03.000Z","msg":"我覺得你地又on99<br />\n以前整電話 無原廠野會話用副廠野<br />\n而家唔出聲就話一換一<br />\n咁同取巧無咩分別姐<br />\n重有咩幾舊水想換原裝野<br />\n原裝真係值幾舊水"},{"pid":"5f8ce97096c6dc235a02c41dc1d92d2925d6a507","tid":261854,"uid":63977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:00:04.000Z","msg":"Apple 咁小家, 點會提供原廠零件俾 d 唔專業既細舖做維修 ?<br />\n一定係假貨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89b6a45a8e296c7c79200ff0023d559649ccab3d","tid":261854,"uid":119718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:02:28.000Z","msg":"樓主做得幾日就咁清楚?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f26d77808f30e6074d20f8746c04fdec2f4b2683","tid":261854,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:04:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Apple 咁小家, 點會提供原廠零件俾 d 唔專業既細舖做維修 ?<br />\n一定係假貨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有次貨既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"830778e5dbc53edbce282160c63a9cf17a320efd","tid":261854,"uid":119562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:06:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主做得幾日就咁清楚?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img sr