在太貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我記得佢報爆外mon換要好似1000左右<br />\n換個外殻又要800<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個價貴過出面好多<br />\n我上華強睇住佢用部機換番個外mon 80人仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係呀 貴到hihi<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁講真, 佢手勢係唔差, 但未至於要咁貴 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b9cfbed678e2129c06bd1a85a0701331d6c6713","tid":261854,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T11:50:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>換mon 我都自己換過， 都係上華強北買塊總成返黎自己換<br />\n<br />\n老豆想換部6 plus 舊電， 有咩牌子推薦？</blockquote><br />\n你想要原定副廠，我華強個邊有幾間信譽幾好既介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n原既話最好啦 但係咪真係原先<br />\n<br />\n副廠係大牌子我都唔介意</blockquote><br />\n巴打... 求介紹呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca31556d4dfc12bb34225c3ad7c52ec2a480daa0","tid":261854,"uid":119562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T13:20:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都係自己淘寶粒iphone 6電黎換<br />\n百幾蚊搞掂，好過出去畀人換假原廠電</blockquote><br />\n自己熟手謝話姐， <span style=\"color: red;\">唔</span>熟手分分鍾整壞埋<span style=\"color: red;\">部</span>手機</blockquote>"},{"pid":"20d880599c3ab9af5ab44b5e28498d13d43002f4","tid":261854,"uid":45897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T14:07:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>之前整過<br />\n佢又係扮晒原廠Mon<br />\n整完之後個mon接觸完全唔良好<br />\n佢仲好意思話係我部機問題<br />\n整之前只不過係有裂痕<br />\n整完之後打字都打唔到<br />\n嬲到我死<br />\n好啦之後要求佢再整過<br />\n佢就求求其其螺絲都唔鑲返上去<br />\n之後係另外一間再整<br />\n嗰個人仲話未見過有人咁樣整電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係原廠Mon都算啦<br />\n最緊要係一個咁有經驗整左咁多部電話嘅人可以講大話<br />\n仲要呃學生妹<br />\n真係好衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前幫襯嗰間係新北江嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n𢇁打 最後佢有冇幫你整返好？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無！<br />\n我見佢第二次整到求求其其咁，覺得再整多次佢一定會偷偷整爛我部機<br />\n最後去左元朗整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbf68a2643e4f247ae3a4a4c547668ad0eff5f30","tid":261854,"uid":23677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T14:10:42.000Z","msg":"幾日前幫個同學部ipad 換玻璃, 佢話之前心急拎去ssp搞, 整完之後個home制鬆左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住我拆機既時候發現入面唔見左好多粒螺絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n塊玻璃都係高仿玻璃黎, 個HOME制撳落怪怪地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24ac791787c4a952b4d65be8b9029622b2c669bc","tid":261854,"uid":1085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T14:31:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e007216213832ed114946ae6eb3815017fc2bb01","tid":261854,"uid":119562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T15:02:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>圖都冇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n圖就冇架啦你可以唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"635208b1b7b9173b17d243922260bf7f23882879","tid":261854,"uid":119562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T15:04:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾日前幫個同學部ipad 換玻璃, 佢話之前心急拎去ssp搞, 整完之後個home制鬆左出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住我拆機既時候發現入面唔見左好多粒螺絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n塊玻璃都係高仿玻璃黎, 個HOME制撳落怪怪地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f1ee8382c66fb45a6ace3a3036020f45e2ff3b","tid":261854,"uid":119562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T15:05:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>之前整過<br />\n佢又係扮晒原廠Mon<br />\n整完之後個mon接觸完全唔良好<br />\n佢仲好意思話係我部機問題<br />\n整之前只不過係有裂痕<br />\n整完之後打字都打唔到<br />\n嬲到我死<br />\n好啦之後要求佢再整過<br />\n佢就求求其其螺絲都唔鑲返上去<br />\n之後係另外一間再整<br />\n嗰個人仲話未見過有人咁樣整電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔係原廠Mon都算啦<br />\n最緊要係一個咁有經驗整左咁多部電話嘅人可以講大話<br />\n仲要呃學生妹<br />\n真係好衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之前幫襯嗰間係新北江嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n𢇁打 最後佢有冇幫你整返好？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無！<br />\n我見佢第二次整到求求其其咁，覺得再整多次佢一定會偷偷整爛我部機<br />\n最後去左元朗整<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁佢有冇退返錢比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8aafd00a88edc06dfaf6cd39445c59236d7489c","tid":261854,"uid":89111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T17:12:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>但上次去屯門個間換玻璃 我睇住佢整<br />\n佢真係換返原本個液晶俾我<br />\n係咪我好彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你又知係原來個塊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我睇住佢換嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ⋯</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁姐係睇住佢換就冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb3d3ae4f179ba87d547c16c21385bff2645a006","tid":261